    <item>
      <title>随着利润大幅下滑，美国银行债券交易员的业绩出现意外下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/bofa-bond-traders-post-surprise-drop-as-profit-slumps-by-half</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行(Bank of America Corp.)的盈利未达到预期，因为该行第四季度的众多费用削减了利润，而且该公司的固定收益交易员的收入意外下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/bofa-bond-traders-post-surprise-drop-as-profit-slumps-by-half</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:04:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德卷土重来总资产突破10万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/blackrock-total-assets-top-10-trillion-after-comeback-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司(BlackRock Inc.)的客户在第四季度纷纷买入其长期基金，向ETF和其他产品增持了630亿美元，这表明随着股票和债券市场的飙升，投资者开始投入现金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/blackrock-total-assets-top-10-trillion-after-comeback-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于需求困难，中国的贷款增长跌至历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/china-s-credit-expansion-slows-in-december-on-lackluster-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于商业信心疲软继续打压借贷需求，12 月份中国贷款增速创有记录以来最慢。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/china-s-credit-expansion-slows-in-december-on-lackluster-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 09:44:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
